{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "华华凤借天时安排众人行动，卢九、顾道人、乔老三、段玉、王飞等人围绕凤林寺与顾道人酒馆追索真相。花夜来的偷盗、卢小云之死、铁水遇害和青龙会布局逐渐串联起来。众人对段玉的怀疑开始松动，段玉也从被动受困转为共同破局。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒真是天公作美。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你喜欢下雨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别的时候不喜欢，现在这场雨却下得正是时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是这场雨一下，问题就全都解决了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们为什么不先到楼外楼吃了饭再去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家最好多买几个蛋，在路上吃。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们现在就动身？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在时候已经不早了，路却并不近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那地方究竟在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在那边。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我去找条大船，我们先坐船去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还像个女贼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你当然不像女贼了，只不过像是个女暴君。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "王飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "王飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道他……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘘——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "砰",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花夜来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_fei",
      "speaker_name": "王飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是骗人的，完全都是骗人的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这样做，只不过是在试探试探你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "试探我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你看出来没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只有一样了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你猜他还在不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我在生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我心里不高兴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不高兴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若是我，你会不会高兴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你准备怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "包子还没有臭。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你被谁骗了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "被我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他的确是被我骗得白滚了一个晚上，可是这件衣服……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "衣服上当然不会长出脚来的，你身上却有脚。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还没有回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还没有回去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "幸好这里还有酒，喝两杯驱驱寒气如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不是来喝酒的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不来喝酒，来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来杀人。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来杀人，杀谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是来杀他的？你明明知道杀人的真凶并不是他！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "卢九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确不愿与段飞熊结仇，但杀子之仇，也不能不报。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "卢九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕杀错了人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不怕别人杀错了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我喝酒一向只是用酒杯喝的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么会知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他毕竟是我的儿子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你才故意用这法子，激他出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是，你怎么会知道他在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也听到我说，他身上穿的，就是我的衣服。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽然已年老多病，耳朵却还不聋。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "非但一点也不聋，简直比……我还灵。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "比兔子还灵",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "卢小云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还不肯说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你还有些什么说不出来的苦衷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看出了谁有可疑之处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顾道人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我怎么看不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为你根本不知道他是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是他刚才却连一句怨言都没有发。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 588,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我才觉得奇怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "卢九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的这个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青龙会在这里的龙抬头老大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本来就只有这一个人，真的希望段玉死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道顾道人就是龙抬头老大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我要说的，全部被你们说了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "卢九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不在。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道他不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "顾道人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，果然有两手，看来我倒真的一直低估了你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你本不该到这里来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自己也知道，可是我却非来不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 696,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为卢小云没有死，你也没有死。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不死，你就要死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道已承认你就是这里的龙抬头老大？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，我又何必再否认。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道本就是来求死的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 714,
      "line_end": 714
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花夜来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "卢小云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你已杀了她灭口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你想替她报仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我杀了她，你本该感激我的，我……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他不该死，难道是你该死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 754,
      "line_end": 754
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确是该死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 756,
      "line_end": 756
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们的老板娘呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 776,
      "line_end": 776
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lai_li",
      "speaker_name": "小癞痢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还在睡觉。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 778
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lai_li",
      "speaker_name": "小癞痢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老板呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_lai_li",
      "speaker_name": "小癞痢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也在睡觉。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 816,
      "line_end": 816
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看得出我们的表情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你并不是出来，而是回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 838,
      "line_end": 838
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你究竟想说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 844,
      "line_end": 844
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只不过想告诉你，你的丈夫本不该死的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "该死的难道是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 848,
      "line_end": 848
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的确该死，",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 850,
      "line_end": 850
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 854,
      "line_end": 854
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "花夜来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 856,
      "line_end": 856
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也醉过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 880,
      "line_end": 880
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也曾醉过，可是我却醒得快。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么时候醒的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 890,
      "line_end": 890
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道不可能有意外？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 896,
      "line_end": 896
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "决不可能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 898,
      "line_end": 898
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也知道卢小云决不是顾道人暗算的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "顾道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 906,
      "line_end": 906
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你已想通了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 920,
      "line_end": 920
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么解释？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 922,
      "line_end": 922
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他黯然接着道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 928,
      "line_end": 928
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从这几点，你就能证明我是花夜来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 938,
      "line_end": 938
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人，就是你这种女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 940,
      "line_end": 940
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我为什么要杀他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 942,
      "line_end": 942
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "女道士",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "感情，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 978,
      "line_end": 978
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然你现在提起了这件事，我也想起了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 990,
      "line_end": 990
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 992,
      "line_end": 992
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他笑了笑，接道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 996,
      "line_end": 996
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1000,
      "line_end": 1000
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "青龙会若是真有那样的冒失鬼，青龙会也就不可怕了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1002,
      "line_end": 1002
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这既然是你赢的，你就该拿走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1006,
      "line_end": 1006
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1010,
      "line_end": 1010
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_ye_lai",
      "speaker_name": "花夜来",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1012,
      "line_end": 1012
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_yu",
      "speaker_name": "段玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1032,
      "line_end": 1032
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四月十五之前，你一定要赶到宝珠山庄去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1034,
      "line_end": 1034
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1036,
      "line_end": 1036
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你明天一早就得走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1038,
      "line_end": 1038
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能不能先让我看看？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1050,
      "line_end": 1050
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "华华凤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这柄刀就是你的订亲礼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    }
